originalText.text: I became a patient of Dr Chen when I moved to New York (many years ago) and it has been the best decision I made. Dr Chen is an expert in his field, highly knowledgeable, kind, and open-minded (willing to listen to patients' concerns). He always makes time for patients if needed and availability has never been issue. Dr Chen genuinely cares for his patients and I can wholeheartedly recommend him (he changed my life for the better).

originalText.text:
I'm not sure how the number of days a week a doctor chooses to see patients has anything to do with their credentials or their ability to provide care.

Dr. Chen has been a phenomenal doctor for me. I can't speak to how other people operate, but I make my appointments in advance and have never, ever had any scheduling or availability issues with him.
